These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Sport   | swimming | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: snooker, poker
1. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person playing poker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Game   | poker | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, electronic
1. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
2. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
3. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
